2.5.20  7:51 am   Hi, I'm 21 and I don't know what to do with my life. I want to do everything in the world but I'm both aware of the limitation of time & resources I was born with and that makes me afraid of starting/risking anything. One thing constant is my interest in arts and music. I don't know shit about both, especially music except for like chords and stuff but I want to learn more. How to learn when all I have are my phone (with keyboard app installed) and my unexperienced and seemingly unteachable right ear? (technically deaf on my left)

     learning happens automatically, as long as you keep thinking, feeling, and exploring

     I love you-well I don't love YOU per se-I just love the YOU you put out on the internet. And your art as well. Thank you, have a nice day!

     holy geneva, you are remarkably forthcoming

2.5.20  7:16 am   Also, what's your favourrite letter/special character?

     i just changed it, to reflect the ongoing changes of life itself

2.5.20  7:09 am   Do you have a life motto?

     yes

     If so what is it?

     i just changed it, to reflect the ongoing changes of life itself

2.5.20  7:02 am   The day didn't go on. You LIED to me

     there must have been some confusion about which day you thought i meant

2.5.20  6:48 am   How do you walk a lime?

     i think it's gonna end up walking you. that's the only way

2.5.20  6:37 am   may I ask some motivating words? I used to be on this high where I want to keep doing things and suddenly I'm back wallowing away.

     now you have me wondering about just what exactly was the nature of those things

2.5.20  6:36 am   How much are you bench pressing at the moment 

     1, maybe 2 benches

2.5.20  6:30 am    How do I harmonize as godly as you can?!

     this may not be what you are expecting, but you have to think about something else besides the notes and chords first. inevitably you will think about the notes and chords quite a bit, because they are awesome, but it almost seems they don't even get their proper fuel for awesomeness without some alterior context to begin with. then the notes and chords will serve to further fuel and strengthen the original context, and so the tale of the day unfolds

2.5.20  6:21 am   When was color invented?

     during the planch epoch, i suspect

2.5.20  6:21 am   do you think we'll eventually run out of questions to ask here?

     no. that's because you're allowed to ask questions that have been already asked hundreds of times before

2.5.20  5:06 am   how do i absolve my sins

     nowadays you can get them on auto-absolve. which of course is a huge sin, which means you'll have to get a competing auto-absolve service, which can in turn be absolved by the first service. and so the balance of life is maintained

     definitely the verse melody was, for sure. that's because it was written by listening to it. it occured in a dream

     Theres just so many wonderful licks and devices in there I cant belive it manages to work but it does. Bravo my dude.

     holy groundswell you are somewhat compassionate

     no, i think that would be phobia of actual phobias. not just the word phobia

2.5.20  2:02 am   It's been a long time since the last update to the reality page. Any plans to add another entry?

     1 is probably not the amount of entries that i would ever plan to add there. that's just not a 1 entry kind of page, if you get what i'm saying

2.5.20  1:58 am   I'm six months pregnant and I just lost my job. I decided to use the spare time to make videos of things to stop the panic and then my computer stopped working. Now there is much panic. How to stop the panic long enough to see something new. Also my baby likes your music. He's into it.

     it seems to me like you should continue to make creations, on a smaller or simplier device. perhaps even whatever device you are using to answer this question. simpler devices actually can often make you stronger creatively. it seems like that was working well for you. and it will probably lead to employment opportunities

2.5.20  1:47 am   hey bill, i'm feeling pretty stressed. any tips?

     you could write some stories, about how you got so stressed. turn it into a folk tale

     thanks for all you do for us

2.4.20  11:20 pm   what was the first ever chord progression that was called a chord progression when it progressed those chords?

     i don't remember, but it led to a lot of other chord sequences and sets of chords also getting called 'progressions', misleading the world at large to think chords are always supposed to 'progress', and overshadowing all of the many ordinary times when chords do not need to 'progress' per se, but exist in all the many other ways
